headline: TransDigm First Quarter Earnings Report and Conference Call Set for Tuesday, February 3, 2026
summary: TransDigm Group Incorporated (NYSE: TDG) today said it will report fiscal 2026 first quarter earnings before the market opens on Tuesday, February 3, 2026.
